data.description: (Price increase reflects new A/C unit, Furnace and dishwasher.) This spectacular townhome is completely remodeled!! Seller invested over $50,000 in upgrades!! Brand new furnace, A/C unit and dishwasher were installed 12/2023. Beautiful new carpet throughout the whole home, completely repainted with new bathroom toilets and sinks. The kitchen shines with its bright freshly painted cupboards, silver hardware and new coriander counter tops.  The oversized deck off the kitchen is perfect for your morning coffee. Enjoy the snowfall cozied up in by the fireplace with oversized windows and vaulted ceilings.  The upstairs bathroom is completely remodeled.  The bedrooms have new closet doors along with new doors throughout the home. The oversized garage has the laundry room and a bonus area with extra storage.  There is a door that leads to your patio, a gate opens up to more grass and privacy as there are no units behind you. Award winning Cherry Creek Schools, easy access to highway, plenty of restaurants and shopping right around the corner!! This home is bright, beautiful and move in ready! It's a must see!!! Showings start 12/19.
